window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Rage Wars are over. Society has fallen. Untold millions are dead.</b></p> <p>The survivors are faced with a horrible, chaotic future.</p> <p>Except in the domed city of Altor, where life is safe and good. There is plenty of food and fresh water, and crime is essentially unheard of.</p> <p>But there is a threat to even that oasis of safety. A threat that will come from within the dome.</p> <p>Contains a special note from the author.</p>"; 
